          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1618925264413-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Brush a little <strong>cold water </strong>around the edges of the pastry (this helps to seal the pastry!)</p><p>Fold the pastry over the mixture and press it together with your fingers to seal in the mixture with as little air trapped inside as possible – these are your <strong>pasties</strong></p><p>Prick air holes into the centre of the<strong> pasties</strong> evenly with a fork</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
